{"tid":1412470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母影乜撚野相啊！","createTime":"2019-08-05T06:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:51:35.000Z","uid":5427,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e1fc173d06ede363b05247dbf29d0d736aa2b3a2","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:44:12.000Z","msg":"每次夢遊都會有途人/遊客會用自己電話影9人相<br />\n<br />\n琴晚夢見係觀塘有個黑衫係外圍影相 <br />\n俾人一句「<span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母影乜撚野相啊</span>」插埋去<br />\n我好明白俾人影到既會好緊張<br />\n亦唔想手足俾人影到樣<br />\n但係個個黑衫既反應係佢只係影外圍 冇影人樣<br />\n佢表示佢都有支持反送中明白唔影樣既規矩<br />\n只係件事發生係自己生活既社區<br />\n想影下俾朋友/屋企人睇<br />\n<br />\n希望前線手足將心比己 先禮後兵 <br />\n瞄撚準備先大大力屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346c7a0b32deec4ceaaafe7ea432a8277e87c07e","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"#我罷緊工"},{"pid":"38c42530a67fe9dc1c41d5b848bbc7959831b8db","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"#我罷緊工"},{"pid":"3617b1f0221fd7e340c327eff07bc3c692aa8821","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:44:55.000Z","msg":"#我罷緊工"},{"pid":"64b28e4d5cfac72a7e76fc5a415814512f10da3e","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"#我罷緊工"},{"pid":"540f08b3c2a815c2438af95077985db670df04b1","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:45:22.000Z","msg":"#我罷緊工"},{"pid":"f97d2a98ebcacf4a001ab30a89b4d130940f70aa","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"#我罷緊工"},{"pid":"1e29875a6ba8e3c0dc1f3def22c876e4fac91829","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:46:04.000Z","msg":"#我罷緊工"},{"pid":"27c67c9b3ea27c8d665efc229023056c98ba24eb","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"#我罷緊工"},{"pid":"7e211dd543141c242faf04e190d1aef23a79d29d","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:46:30.000Z","msg":"#我罷緊工"},{"pid":"96c92a9aa884848b2a7b79df6784fab9c42eff2a","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"#我罷緊工"},{"pid":"723578c6f4de491fbf777d71dd6142de58a9fbf4","tid":1412470,"uid":5427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:51:35.000Z","msg":"見到黑衫哥哥仔好無辜咁俾人屌老母<br />\nFeel到佢有小小心淡<br />\n好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然我唔覺得佢會就咁就唔撐大家<br />\n但係俾人屌老母一定個心唔好受<br />\n佢好大機會係叫人黎幫拖<br />\n或者教育既廢老家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}